snippet.title: World League Baseball (PC) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Here are various bits of World League Baseball, a 2023 Korean-made PC baseball game available on Steam by Haegin Co. I love the art style! I go through a few different modes, so here are timestamps if you want to jump to a certain thing:

00:00 Creating our team/Tutorial
02:10 3-inning exhibition game
14:06 Recruit menu and opening some blind boxes
16:10 Team management
19:51 Personal Drills mode

Home run timestamps: 
22:06
